Package org.mitre.provenance.surrogate.sgf

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GenericInvocationFuzzer
    An SGF that will work with any invocation.
    GenericSGF
    A generic surrogate generating function that creates a redacted node of the same type.
    NodePlaceholderInferAll
    A "friendly" SGF that hides as much information as possible, but permits graph connections to exist.
    RandomInferMarker
    This SGF is used for testing and experimentation purposes.
    StringRedactionSurrogateFunction
    Sample surrogate function.
    SurgicalHideAll
    This SGF sets an edge policy of "HIDE ALL" on the matched object.
    SurgicalHideFirst
    This SGF sets the edge vote to HIDE on the matched object.
    SurgicalInferAll
    This SGF votes to INFER all edges on the matched object.
    SurgicalInferFirst  
    SurgicalSGF
    A surgical SGF is one that can be applied to many objects, and that will only take "surgical action" on those objects that match by name.
